1
00:00:02,711 --> 00:00:04,463
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 3211.7.

2
00:00:04,588 --> 00:00:05,965
WE ARE ENTERING
STANDARD ORBIT

3
00:00:06,089 --> 00:00:07,174
ABOUT GAMMA 2,

4
00:00:07,299 --> 00:00:09,259
AN UNINHABITED
PLANETOID

5
00:00:09,384 --> 00:00:11,094
WITH AN AUTOMATIC
COMMUNICATIONS

6
00:00:11,219 --> 00:00:13,597
AND ASTROGATION STATION.

7
00:00:13,722 --> 00:00:14,640
ENSIGN CHEKOV,

8
00:00:14,765 --> 00:00:15,975
LIEUTENANT UHURA, AND I

9
00:00:16,099 --> 00:00:17,518
WILL BEAM DOWN

10
00:00:17,643 --> 00:00:20,270
AND MAKE A ROUTINE CHECK
OF ITS FACILITIES.

11
00:00:20,395 --> 00:00:21,730
STANDARD ORBIT,
CAPTAIN.

12
00:00:21,856 --> 00:00:23,440
GOOD.

13
00:00:25,108 --> 00:00:26,694
MIND THE STORE,
MR. SPOCK.

14
00:00:26,819 --> 00:00:27,361
ACKNOWLEDGED,
CAPTAIN.

15
00:00:27,486 --> 00:00:28,821
LIEUTENANT UHURA,
LET'S GO.

16
00:00:28,946 --> 00:00:30,030
YES, SIR.

17
00:00:38,455 --> 00:00:39,039
ENERGIZE, SCOTTY.

18
00:00:39,164 --> 00:00:40,833
AYE, CAPTAIN.

19
00:00:50,175 --> 00:00:51,677
CAPTAIN...

20
00:00:51,802 --> 00:00:53,679
WHAT HAPPENED?

21
00:00:53,804 --> 00:00:55,263
MUST BE A...

22
00:00:55,389 --> 00:00:57,224
TRANSPORTER
MALFUNCTION.

23
00:00:57,349 --> 00:01:01,061
IT...WAS
A ROUGH TRIP.

24
00:01:01,186 --> 00:01:03,397
THIS ISN'T GAMMA 2.

25
00:01:03,522 --> 00:01:05,649
LOOK AT THE COLOR
OF THAT SKY.

26
00:01:05,774 --> 00:01:08,193
THIS IS THE CRAZIEST
LANDING PAD
I'VE EVER SEEN.

27
00:01:08,318 --> 00:01:09,987
THAT'S A TRINARY SUN.

28
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,615
SCOTT TO BRIDGE.

29
00:01:13,741 --> 00:01:14,241
SPOCK HERE.

30
00:01:14,366 --> 00:01:16,785
MR. SPOCK,
THE CAPTAIN,

31
00:01:16,911 --> 00:01:18,829
LIEUTENANT UHURA,
AND CHEKOV...

32
00:01:18,954 --> 00:01:20,288
THEY VANISHED.

33
00:01:20,414 --> 00:01:22,624
THEY GOT ONTO
THE TRANSPORTER PLATFORM

34
00:01:22,750 --> 00:01:25,419
AND THEY JUST VANISHED.

35
00:01:25,544 --> 00:01:27,379
I PRESUME YOU MEAN
THEY VANISHED IN A MANNER

36
00:01:27,504 --> 00:01:29,172
NOT CONSISTENT
WITH THE USUAL WORKINGS

37
00:01:29,297 --> 00:01:31,008
OF THE TRANSPORTER,
MR. SCOTT.

38
00:01:31,132 --> 00:01:32,509
AYE, OF COURSE
I MEAN THAT.

39
00:01:32,634 --> 00:01:34,261
YOU THINK I'D CALL YOU
IF THEY JUST BEAMED DOWN?

40
00:01:34,386 --> 00:01:36,263
HAVE YOU REVERSED CONTROLS?

41
00:01:36,388 --> 00:01:39,224
I'VE MADE ALL
THE PROPER CHECKS.
THERE WAS NOTHING.

42
00:01:39,349 --> 00:01:41,643
THERE WAS NO FLASH
OF LIGHT, NOTHING.

43
00:01:41,769 --> 00:01:43,102
THEY WERE GONE.

44
00:01:43,228 --> 00:01:44,187
POWER SURGE?

45
00:01:44,312 --> 00:01:45,564
NOT DOWN HERE.

46
00:01:45,689 --> 00:01:46,857
ALL THE DIALS WERE RIGHT

47
00:01:46,982 --> 00:01:48,525
AND THE TRANSPORTER
WAS FUNCTIONING PERFECTLY.

48
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:50,569
RECHECK YOUR EQUIPMENT,
MR. SCOTT.

49
00:01:50,694 --> 00:01:53,196
I'LL SCAN FOR THEM
ON THE PLANET'S SURFACE.

50
00:01:53,321 --> 00:01:54,197
SPOCK OUT.

51
00:01:54,322 --> 00:01:55,866
BUT, CAPTAIN,
IF WE'RE NOT
ON GAMMA 2,

52
00:01:55,991 --> 00:01:58,911
THEN WHERE ARE WE?

53
00:01:59,036 --> 00:02:00,788
THAT'S WHAT
I'D LIKE TO KNOW.

54
00:02:00,913 --> 00:02:02,497
KIRK TO "ENTERPRISE."

55
00:02:03,415 --> 00:02:04,959
KIRK TO "ENTERPRISE."

56
00:02:08,295 --> 00:02:09,379
DEAD.

57
00:02:11,048 --> 00:02:12,507
MINE, TOO.

58
00:02:12,633 --> 00:02:13,759
CAPTAIN...

59
00:02:13,884 --> 00:02:14,635
LOOK.

60
00:02:15,928 --> 00:02:17,554
PHASERS...ON STUN.

61
00:02:32,861 --> 00:02:34,446
FIRE.

62
00:02:36,865 --> 00:02:37,616
HAND-TO-HAND.

63
00:03:26,790 --> 00:03:29,543
Kirk: SPACE--
THE FINAL FRONTIER.

64
00:03:35,549 --> 00:03:40,137
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP "ENTERPRISE."

65
00:03:40,261 --> 00:03:41,763
ITS 5-YEAR MISSION--

66
00:03:41,889 --> 00:03:44,141
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

67
00:03:44,265 --> 00:03:48,187
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

68
00:03:48,311 --> 00:03:51,231
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

69
00:04:33,356 --> 00:04:37,277
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 3211.8.

70
00:04:37,402 --> 00:04:39,320
WHILE BEAMING DOWN
FROM THE "ENTERPRISE"

71
00:04:39,446 --> 00:04:41,823
TO INSPECT FACILITIES
ON GAMMA 2,

72
00:04:41,949 --> 00:04:43,200
THE NORMAL
TRANSPORTER SEQUENCE

73
00:04:43,324 --> 00:04:44,952
HAS BEEN INTERRUPTED,

74
00:04:45,077 --> 00:04:47,079
AND WE FIND OURSELVES
ON A STRANGE

75
00:04:47,204 --> 00:04:48,663
AND HOSTILE PLANET,

76
00:04:48,789 --> 00:04:51,416
SURROUNDED BY CREATURES
BELONGING TO RACES

77
00:04:51,541 --> 00:04:55,170
SCATTERED ALL THROUGH
THE GALAXY.

78
00:04:55,295 --> 00:04:57,547
EXCELLENT,
CAPTAIN KIRK.

79
00:05:04,179 --> 00:05:06,181
ALTHOUGH
WE EXPECTED STRENGTH

80
00:05:06,306 --> 00:05:08,142
AND COMPETITIVE SPIRIT,

81
00:05:08,267 --> 00:05:11,352
WE ARE GREATLY PLEASED.

82
00:05:11,478 --> 00:05:12,980
EITHER OF YOU HURT?

83
00:05:13,105 --> 00:05:14,856
I DON'T THINK
SO, CAPTAIN.

84
00:05:14,982 --> 00:05:18,110
NOBODY'S HURT, CAPTAIN.
YET.

85
00:05:18,235 --> 00:05:22,990
ADMIRABLE, CHEKOV.
ADMIRABLE.

86
00:05:23,115 --> 00:05:25,575
YOU ALSO, UHURA.

87
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:29,288
YOUR SPIRIT
IS AS GREAT
AS THE CAPTAIN'S.

88
00:05:29,412 --> 00:05:33,292
I CAN SEE
YOU WILL ALL PROVE
INVALUABLE HERE.

89
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:34,584
I AM GALT,

90
00:05:34,709 --> 00:05:38,337
MASTER THRALL
OF THE PLANET
TRISKELION.

91
00:05:40,132 --> 00:05:42,968
I HAVE BEEN SENT
TO WELCOME YOU.

92
00:05:47,139 --> 00:05:50,349
THERE, CAPTAIN.

93
00:05:50,475 --> 00:05:52,227
NOW YOU ARE PREPARED
FOR YOUR TRAINING.

94
00:05:52,351 --> 00:05:54,353
HOW DO YOU KNOW
OUR NAMES?

95
00:05:54,479 --> 00:05:56,982
THE PROVIDERS
WERE EXPECTING YOU,
CAPTAIN.

96
00:05:57,107 --> 00:05:59,651
THEY ARRANGED
YOUR TRANSPORTATION.

97
00:05:59,776 --> 00:06:01,653
THESE PROVIDERS
OF YOURS, ARE THEY--

98
00:06:01,778 --> 00:06:03,362
CORRECTION, CAPTAIN.

99
00:06:03,488 --> 00:06:04,948
THE PROVIDERS
ARE NOT OURS.

100
00:06:05,073 --> 00:06:08,367
WE ARE THEIRS.

101
00:06:08,493 --> 00:06:10,329
WHAT DO THEY WANT
FROM US?

102
00:06:10,453 --> 00:06:13,248
YOU ARE TO BE TRAINED,
OF COURSE.

103
00:06:13,372 --> 00:06:16,001
WHAT OTHER USE IS THERE
FOR THRALLS?

104
00:06:16,126 --> 00:06:17,211
THRALLS?

105
00:06:19,254 --> 00:06:20,379
YOU MUST BE MISTAKEN.

106
00:06:22,341 --> 00:06:23,884
WE'RE OFFICERS...

107
00:06:24,009 --> 00:06:25,219
OF A UNITED SPACESHIP...

108
00:06:25,344 --> 00:06:27,095
ON FEDERATION BUSINESS.

109
00:06:27,221 --> 00:06:29,681
THERE HAS BEEN NO MISTAKE.

110
00:06:29,806 --> 00:06:33,977
YOUR OLD TITLES
MEAN NOTHING HERE,
CAPTAIN.

111
00:06:34,102 --> 00:06:35,603
YOU ARE THRALLS NOW.

112
00:06:37,939 --> 00:06:38,732
YOU ARE TO BE TAKEN

113
00:06:38,857 --> 00:06:39,816
TO THE TRAINING
ENCLOSURE.

114
00:06:39,941 --> 00:06:41,776
[BUZZ]

115
00:06:42,986 --> 00:06:45,072
COME.

116
00:06:45,197 --> 00:06:47,615
PLACES HAVE BEEN
PREPARED FOR YOU.

117
00:06:50,118 --> 00:06:53,663
WE'RE NOT
GOING ANYWHERE...

118
00:06:53,788 --> 00:06:54,539
UNTIL WE HAVE
SOME INFORMATION.

119
00:06:54,664 --> 00:06:55,749
WHO ARE YOU?

120
00:06:55,874 --> 00:06:58,335
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?

121
00:06:58,459 --> 00:06:59,961
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING TO
DO WITH US?

122
00:07:00,087 --> 00:07:03,548
I AM GALT,
THE MASTER THRALL.

123
00:07:03,673 --> 00:07:06,134
THIS PLACE IS
THE PLANET TRISKELION.

124
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,719
YOU ARE TO BE TRAINED

125
00:07:07,844 --> 00:07:10,264
AND SPEND THE REST
OF YOUR LIVES HERE.

126
00:07:27,197 --> 00:07:28,365
MR. SPOCK...

127
00:07:28,489 --> 00:07:30,117
I'VE CHECKED
THAT TRANSPORTER

128
00:07:30,242 --> 00:07:31,326
FROM ONE END
TO THE OTHER.

129
00:07:31,451 --> 00:07:33,453
EVERY CIRCUIT
WORKS PERFECTLY.

130
00:07:33,578 --> 00:07:34,621
WHATEVER THAT
POWER SURGE WAS,

131
00:07:34,746 --> 00:07:36,748
IT HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE TRANSPORTER

132
00:07:36,873 --> 00:07:38,959
OR WITH ANY OTHER
SYSTEM ABOARD THIS SHIP.

133
00:07:39,084 --> 00:07:40,627
I'M BEGINNING
TO BELIEVE THAT,
MR. SCOTT.

134
00:07:40,752 --> 00:07:43,255
I'VE CONDUCTED
TWO SWEEPS OF
THE PLANET'S SURFACE.

135
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:45,966
THERE IS NO
SIGN OF LIFE.

136
00:07:46,091 --> 00:07:48,218
THEN WHAT THE DEVIL
IS HAPPENING?

137
00:07:48,343 --> 00:07:49,177
DOES THAT MEAN
THEIR ATOMS

138
00:07:49,303 --> 00:07:51,554
ARE JUST
FLOATING AROUND
OUT THERE?

139
00:07:51,679 --> 00:07:53,014
NO, DOCTOR.
EVEN THAT

140
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,641
WOULD SHOW UP
ON OUR SENSORS.

141
00:07:54,766 --> 00:07:56,351
WHERE ARE THEY THEN?

142
00:07:56,476 --> 00:07:58,353
THE ONLY ANSWERS
ARE NEGATIVE.

143
00:07:58,478 --> 00:07:59,479
NO MAGNETIC STORMS,

144
00:07:59,604 --> 00:08:00,647
NO IONIC
INTERFERENCE,

145
00:08:00,772 --> 00:08:04,025
NO BREAKDOWN
IN YOUR EQUIPMENT.

146
00:08:04,151 --> 00:08:05,902
A NEGATIVE ATTITUDE
IS NO GOOD TO US.

147
00:08:06,027 --> 00:08:09,489
WE CAN'T JUST
LEAVE THEM
OUT THERE,

148
00:08:09,614 --> 00:08:10,949
WHEREVER THEY ARE.

149
00:08:11,074 --> 00:08:13,160
WE SHALL CONTINUE
SENSOR SCANS, DOCTOR.

150
00:08:13,285 --> 00:08:15,203
AT THE MOMENT,
THAT IS ALL WE CAN DO,

151
00:08:15,329 --> 00:08:18,457
EXCEPT HOPE FOR
A RATIONAL EXPLANATION.

152
00:08:18,581 --> 00:08:21,084
HOPE?

153
00:08:21,209 --> 00:08:23,128
I ALWAYS THOUGHT THAT WAS
A HUMAN FAILING,

154
00:08:23,253 --> 00:08:24,004
MR. SPOCK.

155
00:08:24,129 --> 00:08:25,880
TRUE, DOCTOR.

156
00:08:26,006 --> 00:08:27,257
CONSTANT EXPOSURE

157
00:08:27,382 --> 00:08:29,050
DOES RESULT IN
A CERTAIN DEGREE

158
00:08:29,176 --> 00:08:30,635
OF CONTAMINATION.

159
00:08:35,223 --> 00:08:38,893
THESE ARE YOUR QUARTERS.

160
00:08:39,019 --> 00:08:40,645
OPEN, THRALLS.

161
00:08:51,614 --> 00:08:53,116
AAH!

162
00:08:59,456 --> 00:09:00,415
AAH!

163
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:02,000
AAH!

164
00:09:21,353 --> 00:09:24,523
THAT WAS FOOLISH,
CAPTAIN.

165
00:09:24,689 --> 00:09:27,275
ESCAPE IS
QUITE IMPOSSIBLE...

166
00:09:27,401 --> 00:09:30,820
AS DEMONSTRATED
BY YOUR COLLARS
OF OBEDIENCE.

167
00:09:31,321 --> 00:09:33,990
RETURN TO
YOUR QUARTERS.

168
00:10:06,606 --> 00:10:09,943
THEY ARE NOT
WITHIN THE CONFINES
OF THIS SOLAR SYSTEM.

169
00:10:10,068 --> 00:10:11,486
IT'S BEEN
NEARLY AN HOUR.

170
00:10:11,611 --> 00:10:13,572
CAN PEOPLE
LIVE THAT LONG AS
DISASSEMBLED ATOMS

171
00:10:13,696 --> 00:10:15,656
IN A TRANSPORTER
BEAM?

172
00:10:15,782 --> 00:10:19,119
I HAVE NEVER HEARD OF
THE STUDY BEING DONE,

173
00:10:19,244 --> 00:10:21,829
BUT IT WOULD BE
A FASCINATING PROJECT.

174
00:10:21,955 --> 00:10:23,790
FASCINATING?

175
00:10:23,915 --> 00:10:25,292
THOSE PEOPLE ARE
FRIENDS OF OURS
OUT THERE,

176
00:10:25,417 --> 00:10:26,334
IF THEY'RE STILL ALIVE.

177
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:27,085
PRECISELY.

178
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:28,628
THE ODDS ARE NOT GOOD.

179
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:30,922
NO. I WOULD SAY
APPROXIMATELY 400--

180
00:10:31,047 --> 00:10:32,591
DON'T QUOTE ODDS
AND DON'T GIVE ME

181
00:10:32,715 --> 00:10:34,968
ANY MORE DISPASSIONATE
LOGIC, MR. SPOCK.

182
00:10:35,093 --> 00:10:36,177
JUST KEEP LOOKING
FOR THEM.

183
00:10:36,303 --> 00:10:38,012
I WOULD WELCOME
A SUGGESTION, DOCTOR,

184
00:10:38,138 --> 00:10:39,139
EVEN AN EMOTIONAL ONE,

185
00:10:39,264 --> 00:10:41,600
AS TO WHERE TO LOOK.

186
00:10:44,811 --> 00:10:48,148
FIRST TIME YOU'VE EVER
ASKED ME FOR ANYTHING,

187
00:10:48,273 --> 00:10:50,442
AND IT HAS TO BE
AN OCCASION LIKE THIS.

188
00:10:55,113 --> 00:10:57,115
Chekov: CAPTAIN,
THE ENTERPRISE.

189
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,909
THEY WILL BE TRYING
TO FIND US, WON'T THEY?

190
00:11:00,034 --> 00:11:02,662
THEY'LL TRY, BUT WHERE
DO THEY LOOK?

191
00:11:02,787 --> 00:11:04,998
WE'RE HERE, AND WE DON'T KNOW
WHERE IT IS.

192
00:11:05,123 --> 00:11:07,959
THIS SYSTEM'S STAR
IS A TRINARY.

193
00:11:08,084 --> 00:11:09,461
LIMITS IT A BIT,
BUT WE'RE A LONG WAY

194
00:11:09,586 --> 00:11:11,879
FROM THE "ENTERPRISE,"

195
00:11:12,005 --> 00:11:13,798
IF WE'RE EVEN
IN THE SAME DIMENSION.

196
00:11:22,641 --> 00:11:24,934
I AM YOUR
DRILL THRALL.

197
00:11:25,059 --> 00:11:26,645
I AM CALLED LARS.

198
00:11:26,769 --> 00:11:27,770
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM HER?

199
00:11:27,895 --> 00:11:30,357
THAT IS NOT
YOUR CONCERN.

200
00:11:30,482 --> 00:11:32,567
YOUR DRILL THRALLS WILL
ATTEND YOU PRESENTLY.

201
00:11:35,694 --> 00:11:37,405
THERE IS LITTLE TIME.

202
00:11:41,201 --> 00:11:42,035
Uhura:
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

203
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:45,539
AAH! AAH!
GET OUT!

204
00:11:45,664 --> 00:11:48,124
I HAVE BEEN
SELECTED FOR YOU.

205
00:11:48,249 --> 00:11:50,001
LIEUTENANT,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

206
00:11:50,126 --> 00:11:52,253
[STRUGGLING]

207
00:11:52,379 --> 00:11:53,921
AAH!

208
00:11:54,047 --> 00:11:55,340
LIEUTENANT!

209
00:11:55,465 --> 00:11:57,925
LIEUTENANT, ARE YOU
ALL RIGHT?

210
00:11:58,051 --> 00:11:59,260
LIEUTENANT,
ANSWER ME!

211
00:11:59,386 --> 00:12:00,970
AAH!

212
00:12:01,095 --> 00:12:02,389
LIEUTENANT!

213
00:12:02,514 --> 00:12:04,391
WHAT'S HAPPENING
TO LIEUTENANT UHURA?!

214
00:12:11,356 --> 00:12:12,440
LIEUTENANT,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

215
00:12:13,983 --> 00:12:16,611
IT IS NOT ALLOWED
TO REFUSE SELECTION.

216
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,447
[BEEP]

217
00:12:25,412 --> 00:12:26,663
STEP AWAY
FROM THE DOOR.

218
00:12:28,747 --> 00:12:29,583
[BEEP]

219
00:12:31,042 --> 00:12:32,544
COME.

220
00:12:32,669 --> 00:12:34,212
IT IS THE NOURISHMENT
INTERVAL.

221
00:12:50,144 --> 00:12:51,646
CAPTAIN'S LOG,

222
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:54,691
STARDATE 3259.2.

223
00:12:54,815 --> 00:12:57,444
FIRST OFFICER SPOCK
IN COMMAND.

224
00:12:57,569 --> 00:12:59,613
THE CAPTAIN,
LIEUTENANT UHURA,

225
00:12:59,738 --> 00:13:01,239
AND ENSIGN CHEKOV

226
00:13:01,364 --> 00:13:03,866
HAVE BEEN MISSING
FOR NEARLY TWO HOURS.

227
00:13:03,991 --> 00:13:05,619
COMPUTER
PROBABILITY PROJECTIONS

228
00:13:05,744 --> 00:13:06,827
ARE USELESS

229
00:13:06,953 --> 00:13:08,787
DUE TO INSUFFICIENT DATA.

230
00:13:08,913 --> 00:13:11,165
MR. SPOCK, I'M GETTING
A FLUCTUATING ENERGY READING

231
00:13:11,291 --> 00:13:12,667
ON THIS HYDROGEN CLOUD.

232
00:13:15,754 --> 00:13:16,963
IT'S FAINT, SIR,

233
00:13:17,088 --> 00:13:18,548
BUT IT CONSISTENTLY
READS IN EXCESS

234
00:13:18,673 --> 00:13:20,967
OF PREDICTABLE
ENERGY LEVEL.

235
00:13:21,092 --> 00:13:23,428
INTERESTING.

236
00:13:23,553 --> 00:13:26,640
THERE SEEMS TO BE
AN IONIZATION TRAIL.

237
00:13:26,765 --> 00:13:27,974
WHAT WOULD ACCOUNT
FOR THAT, SPOCK?

238
00:13:28,099 --> 00:13:31,936
EXACTLY THE QUESTION
I HAVE JUST FED TO
THE COMPUTERS, DOCTOR.

239
00:13:32,061 --> 00:13:33,521
AND THE ANSWER IS...

240
00:13:36,566 --> 00:13:38,610
NOTHING KNOWN TO US
WOULD ACCOUNT FOR IT.

241
00:13:38,735 --> 00:13:40,861
WELL, THE TRANSPORTER
HAS NEITHER THE POWER

242
00:13:40,987 --> 00:13:42,530
NOR THE RANGE
TO ACCOUNT FOR THAT.

243
00:13:44,616 --> 00:13:46,409
PLOT A FOLLOW COURSE,
ENSIGN HAINES.

244
00:13:46,534 --> 00:13:48,035
AYE, SIR.

245
00:13:48,161 --> 00:13:50,705
YOU'RE GOING
TO LEAVE HERE
WITHOUT THEM

246
00:13:50,829 --> 00:13:52,332
AND RUN OFF ON SOME
WILD GOOSE CHASE

247
00:13:52,457 --> 00:13:54,334
HALFWAY ACROSS
THE GALAXY

248
00:13:54,459 --> 00:13:56,919
JUST BECAUSE
YOU FOUND A DISCREPANCY
IN A HYDROGEN CLOUD?

249
00:13:57,044 --> 00:13:58,505
DOCTOR,
I AM CHASING THE CAPTAIN,

250
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:00,881
LIEUTENANT UHURA,
AND ENSIGN CHEKOV,

251
00:14:01,007 --> 00:14:02,425
NOT SOME WILD
AQUATIC FOWL.

252
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:04,885
THIS IS THE ONLY LEAD
WE'VE HAD.

253
00:14:05,011 --> 00:14:06,680
COURSE PLOTTED
AND LAID IN,
MR. SPOCK.

254
00:14:06,805 --> 00:14:08,431
310 MARK 241.

255
00:14:08,556 --> 00:14:10,600
INITIATE.
WARP FACTOR 2.

256
00:14:30,036 --> 00:14:33,748
YOU, YOU HAVE BEEN
SELECTED FOR ME?

257
00:14:33,873 --> 00:14:37,460
[DEEP VOICE] NO. I AM
ONLY YOUR DRILL THRALL.

258
00:14:37,585 --> 00:14:39,713
I HAVE
BROUGHT YOU NOURISHMENT.

259
00:14:41,548 --> 00:14:44,217
IT IS A NICE NAME,
CHEE-KOO.

260
00:14:44,342 --> 00:14:47,804
HEH HEH.
CHEKOV.

261
00:14:47,928 --> 00:14:50,348
CHEE-KOOF!

262
00:14:50,473 --> 00:14:52,851
IT IS A VERY NICE NAME.

263
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:55,562
I AM CALLED TAMOON.

264
00:14:55,687 --> 00:15:01,234
OH, PLEASED, PLEASED
TO KNOW YOU, MISS.

265
00:15:04,153 --> 00:15:06,406
YOU ARE A FINE SPECIMEN.

266
00:15:06,531 --> 00:15:08,533
I LIKE YOU BETTER
THAN THE OTHERS.

267
00:15:11,285 --> 00:15:13,329
I WILL
INSTRUCT YOU WELL,

268
00:15:13,454 --> 00:15:16,875
SO MY PROVIDER
WILL TAKE YOU.

269
00:15:16,999 --> 00:15:20,961
THAT'S V-V-VERY KIND
OF YOU, MISS, BUT--

270
00:15:21,087 --> 00:15:23,339
IF MY PROVIDER
IS PLEASED,

271
00:15:23,464 --> 00:15:27,260
WE MAY EVEN BE SELECTED
FOR EACH OTHER.

272
00:15:32,932 --> 00:15:34,893
I DIDN'T REALIZE
I WAS SO HUNGRY.

273
00:15:35,017 --> 00:15:36,436
WHATEVER YOU CALL THIS,
IT WAS VERY GOOD.

274
00:15:36,561 --> 00:15:39,856
IT IS NOURISHMENT.
WE CALL IT THAT.

275
00:15:40,022 --> 00:15:42,024
NOURISHMENT.
THAT'S VERY PRACTICAL.

276
00:15:42,149 --> 00:15:43,651
WHAT DO YOU CALL
THIS COLLAR?

277
00:15:43,777 --> 00:15:45,695
IT IS A SIGN
OF OUR PROVIDER.

278
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:48,615
BY THE COLOR OF THE LIGHTS,
IT CAN BE KNOWN WHO HOLDS US.

279
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,283
WHEN YOU ARE VENDED,
YOU WILL ALSO
HAVE A COLOR.

280
00:15:50,408 --> 00:15:54,995
VENDED? YOU MEAN
BOUGHT, SOLD.

281
00:15:55,121 --> 00:15:57,331
WHEN YOU ARE
DEVELOPED.

282
00:15:57,457 --> 00:15:59,083
THE PROVIDER
WHO OFFERS
THE MOST QUATLOOS

283
00:15:59,208 --> 00:16:01,335
PUTS HIS COLOR ON US.

284
00:16:01,461 --> 00:16:05,089
OUR RACE HAS
ANOTHER NAME FOR IT.

285
00:16:05,214 --> 00:16:06,299
SLAVERY.

286
00:16:08,927 --> 00:16:12,138
THIS...
COLLAR OF OBEDIENCE...

287
00:16:14,724 --> 00:16:19,687
IS GALT THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN OPERATE IT?

288
00:16:19,813 --> 00:16:22,064
IT IS ONLY
TO WARN AND PUNISH.

289
00:16:22,189 --> 00:16:23,357
HOW DOES HE WORK IT?

290
00:16:23,483 --> 00:16:25,318
IT IS NOT PERMITTED
TO TALK OF THAT.

291
00:16:25,443 --> 00:16:28,863
WILL YOU PROVIDE
ALL MY NOURISHMENT?

292
00:16:28,988 --> 00:16:30,239
OF COURSE.

293
00:16:30,364 --> 00:16:32,366
I AM YOUR DRILL THRALL.

294
00:16:32,492 --> 00:16:34,619
I WILL TRAIN YOU WELL.

295
00:16:34,744 --> 00:16:37,288
YES, I'M SURE YOU WILL.

296
00:16:37,413 --> 00:16:38,665
I MUST SAY,

297
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:39,707
I'VE NEVER SEEN
A TOP SERGEANT

298
00:16:39,833 --> 00:16:41,041
WHO LOOKED LIKE YOU.

299
00:16:41,167 --> 00:16:42,710
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

300
00:16:42,836 --> 00:16:45,797
IT MEANS YOU'RE
A VERY BEAUTIFUL WOMAN.

301
00:16:47,089 --> 00:16:48,675
WHAT IS...BEAUTIFUL?

302
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,760
YOU MEAN NOBODY'S EVER
TOLD YOU THAT BEFORE?

303
00:16:51,469 --> 00:16:54,180
WELL, UH,
BEAUTIFUL IS, UM...

304
00:16:55,556 --> 00:16:56,975
BEAUTIFUL...

305
00:16:59,853 --> 00:17:01,562
THAT'S BEAUTIFUL.

306
00:17:05,441 --> 00:17:08,862
SHAHNA,
WHERE WERE YOU BORN?

307
00:17:10,864 --> 00:17:13,115
BORN?

308
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:15,409
I HAVE BEEN HERE
ALWAYS.

309
00:17:15,535 --> 00:17:17,620
YOUR PARENTS--
WHERE ARE THEY?

310
00:17:17,745 --> 00:17:18,788
YOUR MOTHER
AND FATHER.

311
00:17:18,913 --> 00:17:21,290
SHE WHO BORE ME WAS KILLED
IN A FREESTYLE MATCH.

312
00:17:21,415 --> 00:17:22,249
FREESTYLE?

313
00:17:22,375 --> 00:17:23,960
YOU WILL LEARN
ALL THESE THINGS.

314
00:17:25,503 --> 00:17:28,756
LARS AND CHEKOV'S
DRILL THRALL.

315
00:17:28,882 --> 00:17:30,967
THEY WEREN'T BORN HERE.
WHERE DO THEY COME FROM?

316
00:17:31,091 --> 00:17:32,385
IT IS NOT PERMITTED--

317
00:17:36,055 --> 00:17:38,975
THE EXERCISE INTERVAL.

318
00:17:39,099 --> 00:17:41,227
THIS IS YOUR
TRAINING HARNESS.

319
00:17:41,352 --> 00:17:42,436
PUT IT ON.

320
00:17:49,986 --> 00:17:52,154
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

321
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:54,365
NOTHING OUT THERE.
NOTHING OUT THERE
AT ALL.

322
00:17:54,490 --> 00:17:57,243
WE CERTAINLY SEEM
TO BE HEADING INTO
AN EMPTY SECTOR.

323
00:17:57,368 --> 00:17:59,286
PROJECTING BACK
ALONG THE PATH
OF IONIZATION,

324
00:17:59,412 --> 00:18:02,373
THE NEAREST SYSTEM
IS M24 ALPHA.

325
00:18:02,498 --> 00:18:05,960
THAT MUST BE
TWO DOZEN LIGHT YEARS AWAY.

326
00:18:06,085 --> 00:18:08,629
11.630.

327
00:18:08,755 --> 00:18:10,172
ARE YOU SUGGESTING
THAT THEY COULD HAVE
TRANSPORTED

328
00:18:10,297 --> 00:18:13,760
OVER A DISTANCE OF...

329
00:18:13,885 --> 00:18:16,429
YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR
VULCAN MIND, SPOCK.

330
00:18:16,554 --> 00:18:17,972
I'M SUGGESTING NOTHING,
DOCTOR.

331
00:18:18,097 --> 00:18:21,559
I'M MERELY PURSUING
THE ONLY LOGICAL COURSE
AVAILABLE TO US.

332
00:18:25,021 --> 00:18:26,146
HOLD.

333
00:18:30,818 --> 00:18:34,488
THIS THRALL WAS SLOW
IN OBEYING A COMMAND.

334
00:18:34,614 --> 00:18:38,910
FOR HIS PUNISHMENT,
HE WILL BE PRACTICE TARGET.

335
00:18:39,035 --> 00:18:40,578
AS YOU CHARGE,

336
00:18:40,703 --> 00:18:44,206
YOU WILL STRIKE
THE PRACTICE TARGET
WHEN YOU PASS.

337
00:18:44,331 --> 00:18:45,583
YOU BEGIN, UHURA.

338
00:18:49,545 --> 00:18:52,131
NO!

339
00:18:52,256 --> 00:18:56,302
IT IS NOT ALLOWED TO REFUSE
A TRAINING EXERCISE.

340
00:18:56,427 --> 00:18:58,345
I DON'T CARE WHETHER
IT'S ALLOWED OR NOT.

341
00:18:58,471 --> 00:18:59,639
I WILL NOT DO IT.

342
00:18:59,764 --> 00:19:01,181
NONE OF US
WILL DO IT, GALT.

343
00:19:01,307 --> 00:19:03,183
IT IS PART OF YOUR TRAINING.

344
00:19:03,309 --> 00:19:05,561
THE PROVIDERS WISH IT.

345
00:19:05,686 --> 00:19:06,980
THE DEVIL WITH
THE PROVIDERS.

346
00:19:07,105 --> 00:19:08,188
COSSACKS.

347
00:19:11,233 --> 00:19:12,735
[CHOKING]

348
00:19:18,574 --> 00:19:21,995
WE HAVE BEEN TOLERANT
BECAUSE YOU ARE NEWCOMERS,

349
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:24,831
BUT I SEE YOU MUST
BE GIVEN A LESSON.

350
00:19:24,956 --> 00:19:26,040
LARS.

351
00:19:28,334 --> 00:19:30,920
KLOOG.

352
00:19:31,045 --> 00:19:33,547
KLOOG WILL ADMINISTER
CORRECTION.

353
00:19:35,675 --> 00:19:38,886
UHURA, TAKE YOUR PLACE
ON THE TRIAD.

354
00:19:43,223 --> 00:19:44,308
TIE HER.

355
00:19:44,433 --> 00:19:45,768
NO.

356
00:19:46,435 --> 00:19:48,688
NO!

357
00:19:48,813 --> 00:19:50,648
I AM RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE ACTIONS
OF MY PEOPLE.

358
00:19:50,773 --> 00:19:52,358
I DEMAND TO SEE
THE PROVIDERS.

359
00:19:52,483 --> 00:19:54,694
IT IS NOT PERMITTED.

360
00:19:54,819 --> 00:19:58,238
BUT, CAPTAIN,
SINCE YOU ASSUME
RESPONSIBILITY

361
00:19:58,364 --> 00:19:59,365
FOR YOUR PEOPLE,

362
00:19:59,490 --> 00:20:01,617
YOU WILL TAKE
THE PUNISHMENT.

363
00:20:03,577 --> 00:20:07,414
IT IS LESS PAINFUL
THAN THE COLLAR.

364
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:08,875
TURN AROUND.

365
00:20:13,838 --> 00:20:17,424
CAPTAIN, YOU WILL BE
PRACTICE TARGET.

366
00:20:19,552 --> 00:20:22,847
IT IS A SHAME
TO LOSE YOU, CAPTAIN,

367
00:20:22,972 --> 00:20:26,600
BUT IT IS WORTH IT
AS AN EXAMPLE
TO THE OTHERS.

368
00:20:48,372 --> 00:20:49,373
Kirk: CAPTAIN'S LOG,
SUPPLEMENTAL.

369
00:20:49,498 --> 00:20:50,416
STARDATE, UNKNOWN.

370
00:20:50,541 --> 00:20:53,586
OUR STRANGE CAPTIVITY
CONTINUES.

371
00:20:53,711 --> 00:20:56,923
THIS PLANET IS CALLED
TRISKELION.

372
00:20:57,048 --> 00:20:58,841
WE DO NOT KNOW
ITS LOCATION.

373
00:20:58,966 --> 00:21:00,551
WE DO NOT KNOW
WHO CONTROLS IT.

374
00:21:00,676 --> 00:21:02,636
ITS DANGERS...

375
00:21:02,762 --> 00:21:04,555
ARE ABUNDANTLY CLEAR.

376
00:21:26,452 --> 00:21:27,787
HOLD.

377
00:21:31,749 --> 00:21:35,419
REST INTERVAL.
15 TRISECS.

378
00:21:52,979 --> 00:21:54,688
HE'S PRETTY FAST
WITH THAT WHIP.

379
00:21:55,982 --> 00:21:57,650
THIS WILL
STRENGTHEN YOU.

380
00:21:57,775 --> 00:21:58,567
DRINK IT.

381
00:22:03,281 --> 00:22:05,658
KLOOG'S LEFT EYE
IS WEAK.

382
00:22:05,783 --> 00:22:07,326
APPROACH HIM
FROM THAT SIDE.

383
00:22:09,078 --> 00:22:11,664
RESUME PLACES.

384
00:23:21,025 --> 00:23:22,109
Voice: HOLD.

385
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,744
WE HOLD, PROVIDER 1.

386
00:23:31,869 --> 00:23:35,289
PROVIDER 1 BIDS
300 QUATLOOS
FOR THE NEWCOMERS.

387
00:23:35,413 --> 00:23:38,625
PROVIDER 2,
350 QUATLOOS.

388
00:23:38,751 --> 00:23:40,711
PROVIDER 3, 400.

389
00:23:40,836 --> 00:23:42,462
1,000 QUATLOOS.

390
00:23:42,588 --> 00:23:44,631
1,050 QUATLOOS.

391
00:23:44,757 --> 00:23:45,591
2,000.

392
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:57,937
2,000 QUATLOOS ARE BID.

393
00:23:58,062 --> 00:23:59,813
IS THERE A CHALLENGE?

394
00:24:03,650 --> 00:24:07,821
THE NEWCOMERS
HAVE BEEN VENDED
TO PROVIDER 1.

395
00:24:07,947 --> 00:24:09,740
WE'RE FREE PEOPLE.

396
00:24:09,865 --> 00:24:10,950
WE BELONG TO NO ONE.

397
00:24:11,075 --> 00:24:12,743
SUCH SPIRIT.

398
00:24:12,868 --> 00:24:15,579
I WAGER 15 QUATLOOS
THAT HE IS UNTRAINABLE.

399
00:24:15,704 --> 00:24:18,707
20 QUATLOOS THAT
ALL 3 ARE UNTRAINABLE.

400
00:24:18,832 --> 00:24:20,251
5,000 QUATLOOS
THAT THE NEWCOMERS

401
00:24:20,376 --> 00:24:22,460
WILL HAVE
TO BE DESTROYED.

402
00:24:22,586 --> 00:24:25,089
ACCEPTED.
MARK THEM, GALT.

403
00:24:40,062 --> 00:24:44,275
YOU NOW BEAR THE MARK
OF A FINE HERD.

404
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,985
BUT I MUST WARN YOU--

405
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:51,324
ANY FURTHER DISOBEDIENCE
NOW THAT YOU ARE
FULL-FLEDGED THRALLS

406
00:24:51,449 --> 00:24:53,575
WILL BE PUNISHABLE
BY DEATH.

407
00:25:00,916 --> 00:25:02,876
MR. SPOCK, IT JUST
DOESN'T MAKE SENSE

408
00:25:03,002 --> 00:25:03,961
THEY COULD HAVE COME
THIS FAR.

409
00:25:04,086 --> 00:25:06,630
IF THERE'S
ANY CHANCE AT ALL, IT'S
TO CONTINUE TO SEARCH

410
00:25:06,755 --> 00:25:08,299
IN THE AREA THEY WERE LOST.

411
00:25:08,424 --> 00:25:09,675
WE SEARCHED THE AREA.

412
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,802
IT'S ALWAYS POSSIBLE
TO MISS SOMETHING.

413
00:25:11,927 --> 00:25:14,096
SUCH AS A FAILURE IN
THE TRANSPORTER MECHANISM.

414
00:25:14,221 --> 00:25:16,807
NO, SIR.
THERE WAS NO SIGN
OF FAILURE.

415
00:25:16,932 --> 00:25:19,601
THERE WAS NO SIGN OF THEM
IN THE AREA OF GAMMA 2.

416
00:25:19,726 --> 00:25:21,479
IF THEY WEREN'T
THERE, IT'S
JUST RIDICULOUS

417
00:25:21,603 --> 00:25:23,356
TO THINK THEY COULD
STILL BE ALIVE,

418
00:25:23,481 --> 00:25:24,731
NOT AFTER
ALL THIS TIME.

419
00:25:24,857 --> 00:25:26,484
IN THAT CASE, DOCTOR,
WE HAVE NOTHING TO LOSE

420
00:25:26,608 --> 00:25:28,235
BY PURSUING
OUR PRESENT COURSE.

421
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,577
SLOW DOWN.
SLOW DOWN.

422
00:25:37,703 --> 00:25:39,246
WAIT A MINUTE.
WAIT A MINUTE.

423
00:25:39,372 --> 00:25:41,081
WE'VE COVERED
OVER 2 MILES.

424
00:25:41,207 --> 00:25:42,375
CAN WE TAKE A BREATHER?

425
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:43,583
A REST?

426
00:25:43,709 --> 00:25:47,129
OH. VERY WELL.
IF YOU ARE TIRED.

427
00:25:47,254 --> 00:25:48,005
OH.

428
00:25:48,130 --> 00:25:50,049
WELL, IT'S GOOD
TO GET AWAY

429
00:25:50,174 --> 00:25:54,011
FROM THAT
DEVELOPMENT AREA,
EVEN FOR A WHILE.

430
00:25:54,136 --> 00:25:56,972
SHAHNA, WHY DO THE,
UH, PROVIDERS...

431
00:25:57,097 --> 00:25:58,516
WHY DO THEY LIKE

432
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:02,936
TO WATCH OTHERS
BEING HURT...

433
00:26:03,062 --> 00:26:04,730
KILLED?

434
00:26:06,148 --> 00:26:09,527
THAT IS THE WAY.

435
00:26:09,651 --> 00:26:12,946
THEIR VOICES SOUND...
MECHANICAL.

436
00:26:13,072 --> 00:26:15,032
ARE THEY COMPUTERS?

437
00:26:15,157 --> 00:26:16,325
COMPUTERS?

438
00:26:21,163 --> 00:26:23,374
YOU'VE SEEN THEM.

439
00:26:23,499 --> 00:26:25,792
DO THEY HAVE BODIES?

440
00:26:25,918 --> 00:26:27,669
NOT SUCH AS OURS.

441
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:33,509
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?

442
00:26:33,633 --> 00:26:35,135
IT IS NOT USED.

443
00:26:36,262 --> 00:26:38,596
IT'S VERY OLD.
DOES IT HAVE A NAME?

444
00:26:41,934 --> 00:26:43,519
SHAHNA.

445
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:51,609
COULD IT
HAVE BEEN A CITY
FOR THE PROVIDERS?

446
00:26:51,735 --> 00:26:53,487
I DO NOT THINK
IT IS WELL
TO ASK SUCH THINGS.

447
00:26:53,611 --> 00:26:57,824
BUT THEY DO HAVE BODIES,
OR DID HAVE?

448
00:26:57,950 --> 00:27:00,994
ONE DOES NOT TALK
OF SUCH THINGS.

449
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,288
UH...

450
00:27:03,372 --> 00:27:04,873
IT'S VERY PRETTY COUNTRY.

451
00:27:08,085 --> 00:27:11,589
VERY MUCH LIKE
MY HOME PLANET EARTH.

452
00:27:14,133 --> 00:27:15,842
PLANET?

453
00:27:15,968 --> 00:27:18,387
WHERE I WAS BORN.

454
00:27:18,512 --> 00:27:20,306
SHAHNA...

455
00:27:20,431 --> 00:27:22,766
DON'T YOU EVER LOOK
AT THE NIGHT SKY?

456
00:27:22,891 --> 00:27:26,686
THE LIGHTS UP THERE?

457
00:27:26,812 --> 00:27:29,106
I HAVE LOOKED AT THEM.

458
00:27:29,231 --> 00:27:32,443
WELL, THOSE ARE STARS.

459
00:27:32,568 --> 00:27:33,902
AND AROUND THEM...

460
00:27:34,027 --> 00:27:36,447
ARE PLANETS.

461
00:27:36,572 --> 00:27:39,450
AND THERE ARE PEOPLE
THAT LIVE ON THEM,

462
00:27:39,575 --> 00:27:40,909
JUST LIKE US.

463
00:27:42,660 --> 00:27:45,372
HOW CAN ONE LIVE
ON A FLICKER OF LIGHT?

464
00:27:45,498 --> 00:27:48,000
FROM EARTH,
TRISKELION'S 3 SUNS

465
00:27:48,125 --> 00:27:50,544
ARE JUST A FLICKER
OF LIGHT.

466
00:27:53,005 --> 00:27:57,801
ACTUALLY, THIS IS
THE DARKEST PLANET
I'VE EVER SEEN.

467
00:27:57,926 --> 00:27:58,636
DARK?

468
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:02,431
BUT ALL IS LIGHTED.

469
00:28:02,556 --> 00:28:04,766
HERE, THE CHAMBERS.

470
00:28:04,891 --> 00:28:07,727
THE THRALLS
HAVE NO FREEDOM, SHAHNA.

471
00:28:07,853 --> 00:28:09,771
YOU DON'T THINK
OR DO ANYTHING

472
00:28:09,896 --> 00:28:12,358
BUT WHAT THE PROVIDERS
TELL YOU.

473
00:28:12,483 --> 00:28:14,318
WHAT ELSE WOULD ONE DO?

474
00:28:17,530 --> 00:28:19,156
LOVE...

475
00:28:19,281 --> 00:28:20,658
FOR ONE THING.

476
00:28:20,782 --> 00:28:22,826
WHAT IS...LOVE?

477
00:28:22,951 --> 00:28:25,703
LOVE...

478
00:28:25,829 --> 00:28:29,500
IS THE MOST IMPORTANT THING
ON EARTH...

479
00:28:29,625 --> 00:28:32,169
ESPECIALLY TO A MAN
AND A WOMAN.

480
00:28:32,294 --> 00:28:34,171
WE, TOO, HAVE MATES.

481
00:28:34,296 --> 00:28:36,131
WHEN IT IS TIME
TO INCREASE THE HERD,

482
00:28:36,256 --> 00:28:38,217
MY PROVIDER WILL
SELECT ONE FOR ME.

483
00:28:38,342 --> 00:28:40,802
ON EARTH...

484
00:28:40,927 --> 00:28:44,097
WE SELECT OUR OWN MATE.

485
00:28:44,223 --> 00:28:46,392
