WE ARE AWARE
OF YOUR COMPETITIVE
ABILITIES, CAPTAIN.

727
00:41:33,699 --> 00:41:36,035
WELL, THEN...

728
00:41:36,161 --> 00:41:37,245
I WAGER...

729
00:41:39,247 --> 00:41:42,917
THAT WITH WEAPONS
OF YOUR OWN CHOICE,

730
00:41:43,042 --> 00:41:44,710
RIGHT HERE AND NOW,

731
00:41:44,836 --> 00:41:47,964
MY PEOPLE CAN OVERCOME
AN EQUAL NUMBER OF THRALLS

732
00:41:48,089 --> 00:41:49,090
SET AGAINST US.

733
00:41:49,215 --> 00:41:51,592
100 QUATLOOS
ON THE NEWCOMERS.

734
00:41:51,717 --> 00:41:54,053
400 QUATLOOS AGAINST
THE NEWCOMERS.

735
00:41:54,179 --> 00:41:56,222
200 QUATLOOS AGAINST!

736
00:41:56,348 --> 00:41:57,974
500 FOR THE NEWCOMERS.

737
00:41:58,099 --> 00:42:00,018
CONTEST BY MULTIPLE
ELIMINATION.

738
00:42:00,143 --> 00:42:02,687
WAIT! WAIT!
HEAR ME!

739
00:42:02,812 --> 00:42:07,233
WE CAN'T WAGER FOR TRIFLES
LIKE QUATLOOS.

740
00:42:07,359 --> 00:42:08,985
THE STAKES MUST BE HIGHER.

741
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:10,945
NAME YOUR STAKES,
CAPTAIN.

742
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:12,405
IF WE WIN,

743
00:42:12,530 --> 00:42:14,573
THE "ENTERPRISE"
AND ITS CREW

744
00:42:14,699 --> 00:42:16,201
LEAVES HERE IN SAFETY.

745
00:42:16,326 --> 00:42:19,745
FURTHERMORE, ALL THE THRALLS
ON THE PLANET MUST BE FREED.

746
00:42:19,871 --> 00:42:22,123
ANARCHY.
THEY WOULD STARVE.

747
00:42:22,248 --> 00:42:23,291
YOU WILL EDUCATE
AND TRAIN THEM

748
00:42:23,416 --> 00:42:26,378
TO ESTABLISH A NORMAL
SELF-GOVERNING CULTURE.

749
00:42:26,503 --> 00:42:29,839
THRALLS GOVERN THEMSELVES?
RIDICULOUS!

750
00:42:29,964 --> 00:42:31,132
WE HAVE DONE THE SAME

751
00:42:31,257 --> 00:42:34,219
WITH CULTURES
THROUGHOUT THE GALAXY.

752
00:42:34,344 --> 00:42:35,761
ARE YOU WILLING
TO ADMIT

753
00:42:35,887 --> 00:42:37,763
THAT WE CAN DO SOMETHING
YOU CAN'T?

754
00:42:37,889 --> 00:42:39,640
THERE IS NOTHING
WE CANNOT DO!

755
00:42:39,765 --> 00:42:41,518
AND IF YOU LOSE,
CAPTAIN?

756
00:42:43,144 --> 00:42:44,979
IF WE LOSE...

757
00:42:48,358 --> 00:42:49,901
WE WILL REMAIN HERE,

758
00:42:50,026 --> 00:42:51,861
THE ENTIRE CREW
OF THE "ENTERPRISE,"

759
00:42:51,986 --> 00:42:54,613
THE MOST STUBBORN,
DETERMINED COMPETITORS
IN THE UNIVERSE.

760
00:42:54,739 --> 00:42:57,367
WE'LL BECOME THRALLS,
ENTER YOUR GAMES,

761
00:42:57,492 --> 00:42:58,826
OBEY YOUR ORDERS
WITHOUT REBELLION.

762
00:42:58,951 --> 00:43:00,578
YOU'LL BE ASSURED
OF GENERATIONS

763
00:43:00,703 --> 00:43:02,414
OF THE MOST EXCITING
WAGERING YOU'VE EVER HAD.

764
00:43:02,539 --> 00:43:05,166
YOUR STAKES ARE INDEED
HIGH, CAPTAIN.

765
00:43:05,291 --> 00:43:07,668
NOT FOR TRUE GAMESTERS.

766
00:43:07,793 --> 00:43:10,796
WE WILL ACCEPT
YOUR STAKES
ON ONE CONDITION.

767
00:43:10,922 --> 00:43:12,340
NAME IT.

768
00:43:12,465 --> 00:43:13,799
AS LEADER
OF YOUR PEOPLE,

769
00:43:13,925 --> 00:43:16,511
YOUR SPIRIT SEEMS
MOST INDOMITABLE.

770
00:43:16,635 --> 00:43:17,678
WE SUGGEST YOU ALONE,

771
00:43:17,803 --> 00:43:20,557
PITTED AGAINST
3 CONTESTANTS
OF OUR CHOOSING.

772
00:43:23,101 --> 00:43:25,437
3 AGAINST ONE...

773
00:43:25,562 --> 00:43:29,232
THOSE ARE
PRETTY HIGH ODDS.

774
00:43:29,357 --> 00:43:31,443
NOT FOR TRUE
GAMESTERS, CAPTAIN.

775
00:43:31,568 --> 00:43:34,028
YOUR...YOUR TERMS
ARE UNFAIR.

776
00:43:34,153 --> 00:43:36,489
ON THE CONTRARY,
THEY'RE EXTREMELY
FAIR,

777
00:43:36,614 --> 00:43:39,200
SINCE YOUR
ALTERNATIVE
IS DEATH.

778
00:43:41,369 --> 00:43:44,247
WELL, IN THAT CASE,
I'LL ACCEPT YOUR TERMS.

779
00:43:44,372 --> 00:43:46,124
GALT WILL
PREPARE YOU.

780
00:43:52,046 --> 00:43:55,174
Provider: BECAUSE YOU WAGER
YOUR SKILL FOR ALL YOUR PEOPLE,

781
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,175
THEY WILL BE PERMITTED

782
00:43:56,301 --> 00:43:57,218
TO WATCH THE OUTCOME
OF THE GAME

783
00:43:57,343 --> 00:43:59,512
ON THE SHIP'S
VIEW SCREEN.

784
00:43:59,637 --> 00:44:00,805
MR. SPOCK, LOOK!

785
00:44:00,930 --> 00:44:02,723
Provider: CAPTAIN,
YOU WILL DEFEND.

786
00:44:02,848 --> 00:44:05,101
THRALLS MUST STAY
IN THE BLUE AREA.

787
00:44:05,226 --> 00:44:06,311
YOU WILL
TAKE THE YELLOW.

788
00:44:06,436 --> 00:44:07,979
TOUCHING
AN OPPOSING COLOR

789
00:44:08,104 --> 00:44:10,315
DEPRIVES A CONTESTANT
OF ONE WEAPON.

790
00:44:10,440 --> 00:44:12,442
AN OPPONENT
MUST BE KILLED

791
00:44:12,567 --> 00:44:14,486
TO BE REMOVED
FROM THE GAME.

792
00:44:14,611 --> 00:44:17,905
IF ONLY WOUNDED,
HE IS REPLACED
BY A FRESH THRALL.

793
00:44:18,030 --> 00:44:20,199
IS THAT CLEAR, CAPTAIN?

794
00:44:20,325 --> 00:44:22,076
YES, THAT'S CLEAR.

795
00:44:22,201 --> 00:44:24,162
WHAT IN THE NAME
OF HEAVEN IS THIS?

796
00:44:24,287 --> 00:44:26,664
HEAVEN'S GOT VERY LITTLE
TO DO WITH THIS.

797
00:45:39,320 --> 00:45:40,405
SHAHNA.

798
00:45:55,712 --> 00:45:56,921
YOU LIED.

799
00:45:57,046 --> 00:45:58,839
EVERYTHING YOU SAID.

800
00:46:35,334 --> 00:46:39,004
THE THRALLS...
SURRENDER!

801
00:46:43,718 --> 00:46:46,387
Provider: YOU HAVE WON,
CAPTAIN KIRK,

802
00:46:46,512 --> 00:46:48,097
UNFORTUNATELY.

803
00:46:48,222 --> 00:46:50,475
HOWEVER, THE TERMS OF THE WAGER
WILL BE HONORED.

804
00:46:50,600 --> 00:46:52,017
YOU ARE FREE.

805
00:46:55,772 --> 00:46:57,482
REMOVE YOUR COLLARS.

806
00:47:15,625 --> 00:47:17,168
THE THRALLS
WILL BE TRAINED?

807
00:47:17,293 --> 00:47:18,753
THEY WILL BE TRAINED.

808
00:47:18,877 --> 00:47:20,171
WE HAVE SAID IT.

809
00:47:22,965 --> 00:47:23,924
I THINK
YOU'LL FIND IT

810
00:47:24,049 --> 00:47:25,343
A MUCH MORE
EXCITING GAME

811
00:47:25,468 --> 00:47:27,052
THAN THE ONE
YOU'VE BEEN PLAYING.

812
00:47:27,178 --> 00:47:28,929
I'M SORRY, SHAHNA.

813
00:47:29,054 --> 00:47:31,516
I DIDN'T LIE.

814
00:47:31,641 --> 00:47:33,142
I DID
WHAT WAS NECESSARY.

815
00:47:33,267 --> 00:47:34,268
SOMEDAY, I HOPE
YOU'LL UNDERSTAND.

816
00:47:34,393 --> 00:47:37,104
I UNDERSTAND...
A LITTLE.

817
00:47:38,230 --> 00:47:42,109
YOU WILL LEAVE US NOW?

818
00:47:42,234 --> 00:47:43,277
YES.

819
00:47:43,402 --> 00:47:47,198
TO GO BACK TO THE LIGHTS
IN THE SKY?

820
00:47:47,323 --> 00:47:48,240
YES.

821
00:47:48,366 --> 00:47:51,243
I WOULD LIKE TO GO
TO THOSE LIGHTS WITH YOU.

822
00:47:51,369 --> 00:47:52,953
TAKE ME?

823
00:47:53,078 --> 00:47:54,372
I CAN'T.

824
00:47:54,497 --> 00:47:56,207
THEN TEACH ME HOW,

825
00:47:56,332 --> 00:47:58,501
AND I WILL FOLLOW YOU.

826
00:47:58,626 --> 00:48:00,961
THERE'S SO MUCH YOU MUST
LEARN HERE FIRST.

827
00:48:01,086 --> 00:48:03,339
THE PROVIDERS
WILL TEACH YOU.

828
00:48:03,464 --> 00:48:04,632
LEARN IT, SHAHNA.

829
00:48:04,757 --> 00:48:06,718
ALL YOUR PEOPLE
MUST LEARN

830
00:48:06,843 --> 00:48:08,469
BEFORE YOU CAN REACH
FOR THE STARS.

831
00:48:09,970 --> 00:48:11,055
SHAHNA...

832
00:48:32,076 --> 00:48:33,661
SCOTTY!

833
00:48:33,786 --> 00:48:34,620
Scotty:
AYE, SIR.

834
00:48:37,122 --> 00:48:38,750
BEAM US UP.

835
00:49:04,316 --> 00:49:06,235
GOOD-BYE, JIM KIRK.

836
00:49:08,362 --> 00:49:11,240
I WILL LEARN...

837
00:49:11,365 --> 00:49:13,659
AND WATCH THE LIGHTS
IN THE SKY...

838
00:49:16,662 --> 00:49:18,080
AND REMEMBER.
